      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "姚期"
      ],
      "text": "唔！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14001008_e00027",
      "play_id": "14001008",
      "scene_id": "14001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "姚期"
      ],
      "text": "小奴才说的话真是胆大，打死人还说是不犯王法！",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14001008_e00028",
      "play_id": "14001008",
      "scene_id": "14001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "姚期"
      ],
      "text": "儿是好汉？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14001008_e00029",
      "play_id": "14001008",
      "scene_id": "14001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "姚刚"
      ],
      "text": "儿是好汉！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14001008_e00030",
      "play_id": "14001008",
      "scene_id": "14001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "姚期"
      ],
      "text": "是好汉随为父参王见驾，少刻间见万岁谁是谁非，儿要启奏皇家。",
      "text_length": 29
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14001008_e00031",
      "play_id": "14001008",
      "scene_id": "14001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "姚期"
      ],
      "text": "臣姚期见驾，吾皇万岁！",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14001008_e00032",
      "play_id": "14001008",
      "scene_id": "14001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘秀"
      ],
      "text": "姚皇兄，你可知罪？",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14001008_e00033",
      "play_id": "14001008",
      "scene_id": "14001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "姚期"
      ],
      "text": "臣知罪，但不知罪犯何条？",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14001008_e00034",
      "play_id": "14001008",
      "scene_id": "14001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘秀"
      ],
      "text": "你子姚刚，将郭太师剑劈府门，你还不知罪么？",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14001008_e00035",
      "play_id": "14001008",
      "scene_id": "14001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "姚期"
      ],
      "text": "郭老太师也有一行大罪。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14001008_e00036",
      "play_id": "14001008",
      "scene_id": "14001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘秀"
      ],
      "text": "太师何罪之有？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14001008_e00037",
      "play_id": "14001008",
      "scene_id": "14001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "姚期"
      ],
      "text": "他在府门之外，私立三尺禁地，文官下轿，武将离鞍。万岁可曾降旨？",
      "text_length": 31
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14001008_e00038",
      "play_id": "14001008",
      "scene_id": "14001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘秀"
      ],
      "text": "这个……寡人有言在先，未曾降旨。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14001008_e00039",
      "play_id": "14001008",
      "scene_id": "14001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "姚期"
      ],
      "text": "万岁无旨，斩者无亏。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14001008_e00040",
      "play_id": "14001008",
      "scene_id": "14001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘秀"
      ],
      "text": "好个斩者无亏！",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14001008_e00041",
      "play_id": "14001008",
      "scene_id": "14001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "姚刚"
      ],
      "text": "绑坏了！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14001008_e00042",
      "play_id": "14001008",
      "scene_id": "14001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘秀"
      ],
      "text": "呀！殿角下绑的何人？",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14001008_e00043",
      "play_id": "14001008",
      "scene_id": "14001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "姚期"
      ],
      "text": "犬子姚刚。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14001008_e00044",
      "play_id": "14001008",
      "scene_id": "14001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘秀"
      ],
      "text": "内侍快快松绑，不要绑坏了孤的小爱卿。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14001008_e00045",
      "play_id": "14001008",
      "scene_id": "14001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "太监甲松绑。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14001008_e00046",
      "play_id": "14001008",
      "scene_id": "14001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "姚刚"
      ],
      "text": "谢万岁不斩之恩！",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14001008_e00047",
      "play_id": "14001008",
      "scene_id": "14001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘秀"
      ],
      "text": "非是寡人不斩与你。孤王有言在先，姚不反汉，汉不斩姚。命你带领三千人马，镇守湖北宛子城。你父子午门一别，下殿去吧！",
      "text_length": 56
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14001008_e00048",
      "play_id": "14001008",
      "scene_id": "14001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "姚期",
        "姚刚"
      ],
      "text": "谢万岁！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14001008_e00049",
      "play_id": "14001008",
      "scene_id": "14001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "姚刚三笑。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14001008_e00050",
      "play_id": "14001008",
      "scene_id": "14001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "姚期"
      ],
      "text": "奴才！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14001008_e00051",
      "play_id": "14001008",
      "scene_id": "14001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 51,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "姚期"
      ],
      "text": "万岁爷赦了姚霸林，好似枯木又逢春。手拉姣儿下龙廷，开言叫声小霸林：此去湖北要改情性，儿不要提刀乱杀人！",
      "text_length": 51
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14001008_e00052",
      "play_id": "14001008",
      "scene_id": "14001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 52,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "姚期"
      ],
      "text": "儿来看。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14001008_e00053",
      "play_id": "14001008",
      "scene_id": "14001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 53,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "姚刚"
      ],
      "text": "看什么？",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14001008_e00054",
      "play_id": "14001008",
      "scene_id": "14001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 54,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "姚期"
      ],
      "text": "为父的年迈苍苍白如银，",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14001008_e00055",
      "play_id": "14001008",
      "scene_id": "14001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 55,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "叫头",
      "speakers": [
        "姚期"
      ],
      "text": "姚刚，我的儿呀！",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14001008_e00056",
      "play_id": "14001008",
      "scene_id": "14001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 56,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "姚期"
      ],
      "text": "好一似瓦上霜、风前灯，能过几春？",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14001008_e00057",
      "play_id": "14001008",
      "scene_id": "14001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 57,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "姚刚"
      ],
      "text": "爹爹！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14001008_e00058",
      "play_id": "14001008",
      "scene_id": "14001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 58,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "姚刚"
      ],
      "text": "爹爹落泪儿悲伤，点点珠泪洒胸膛。在朝为官有什么好？一点不到有损伤！倒不如修下辞王表，告职回乡享安康。https://scripts.xikao.com/play/140010082022-03-10在午门辞别生身父，回府去拜上老萱堂。",
      "text_length": 117
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14001008_e00059",
      "play_id": "14001008",
      "scene_id": "14001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 59,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "三叫头",
      "speakers": [
        "姚刚"
      ],
      "text": "爹爹！我父！爹爹呀！",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14001008_e00060",
      "play_id": "14001008",
      "scene_id": "14001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 60,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "姚刚下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14001008_e00061",
      "play_id": "14001008",
      "scene_id": "14001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 61,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "三叫头",
      "speakers": [
        "姚期"
      ],
      "text": "姚刚！霸林！哎，我的儿呀！",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14001008_e00062",
      "play_id": "14001008",
      "scene_id": "14001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 62,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "姚期"
      ],
      "text": "金殿去了姚霸林，父子们相会万不能。转过金殿梧桐树，告职回乡乐安宁。",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14001008_e00063",
      "play_id": "14001008",
      "scene_id": "14001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 63,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "姚期"
      ],
      "text": "臣启见万岁！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14001008_e00064",
      "play_id": "14001008",
      "scene_id": "14001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 64,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘秀"
      ],
      "text": "呀，姚皇兄为何去而复返？",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14001008_e00065",
      "play_id": "14001008",
      "scene_id": "14001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 65,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "姚期"
      ],
      "text": "臣启万岁，臣要告职归林。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14001008_e00066",
      "play_id": "14001008",
      "scene_id": "14001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 66,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘秀"
      ],
      "text": "皇兄告职还乡，叫寡人怎能舍得？",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14001008_e00067",
      "play_id": "14001008",
      "scene_id": "14001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 67,
      "seq_in_scene": 67,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "姚期"
      ],
      "text": "要臣在朝伴驾，只须依臣一件。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14001008_e00068",
      "play_id": "14001008",
      "scene_id": "14001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 68,
      "seq_in_scene": 68,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘秀"
      ],
      "text": "哪一件？",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14001008_e00069",
      "play_id": "14001008",
      "scene_id": "14001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 69,
      "seq_in_scene": 69,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "姚期"
      ],
      "text": "万岁戒酒百日，老臣方能在朝伴驾。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14001008_e00070",
      "play_id": "14001008",
      "scene_id": "14001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 70,
      "seq_in_scene": 70,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘秀"
      ],
      "text": "只要皇兄在朝，慢说戒酒百日，就是周年半岁，又待何妨？内侍，搀扶姚皇兄！",
      "text_length": 35
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14001008_e00071",
      "play_id": "14001008",
      "scene_id": "14001008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 71,
      "seq_in_scene": 71,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "太监甲扶姚期起。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "14001008_e00072",
      "play_id": "14001008",
      "scene_id": "14001008_s01",
